OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA rather
OL,6,Fcloudy night with showers, heavy at
OL,7,Ftimes and merging into longer periods
OL,8,Fof rain near the west coast. Fresh
OL,9,Fsouthwest winds, occasionally strong
OL,10,Faround coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA rather cloudy morning with
OL,13,Fscattered showers. Turning brighter
OL,14,Fthrough the afternoon with some
OL,15,Fsunnier spells developing and showers
OL,16,Fbecoming fewer. Brisk winds,
OL,17,Foccasionally strong on the west coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
